{"tid":1793081,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 首爾弘大有手足有嘢同各位手足講！","createTime":"2019-12-22T06:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T07:52:32.000Z","uid":279176,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f79d70f32461269a85d3bc8fec1a1aec4785345b","tid":1793081,"uid":279176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"突發[/b][/b]<br />\n有班人冒住凍都要企係到嗌口號叫大家加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲要叫我地影佢地然後話翻比大家知 <br />\n世界各地都有人撐緊我地叫我地加油唔好放棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpUMCD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpUMCD8.png&h=8589d3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以<strong></strong><br />\n平安夜聖誕倒數元誕出黎啊啊啊嘅啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749e034957bb450f544362a2fae10f484a3dcd91","tid":1793081,"uid":279176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T06:18:15.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604649d5f6982ca708e87a46975ecb8a43bc1764","tid":1793081,"uid":60934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkg